title: 95/484/EC: Council Decision of 30 October 1995 on the conclusion of a Protocol on financial and technical cooperation between the European Community and the Republic of Malta
header:
COUNCIL DECISION
of 30 October 1995
on the conclusion of a Protocol on financial and technical  cooperation between the European Community and the Republic of Malta
(95/484/EC)
THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN UNION
recitals:
,
Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, and in particular Article 238, in  conjunction with Article 228, paragraph 2, second sentence and paragraph 3, second subparagraph  thereof,
Having regard to the proposal from the Commission,
Having regard to the assent of the European Parliament (1),
Whereas the Protocol on financial and technical cooperation between the European Community and the  Republic of Malta should be approved,
main_body:
The Protocol on financial and technical cooperation between the  European Community and the Republic of Malta is hereby approved on behalf of the Community.
The text of the Protocol is attached to this Decision.
The President of the Council shall give the notification provided for in Article 21 of  the Protocol (2).
attachments:
Done at Luxembourg, 30 October 1995.
For the Council
The President
J. SOLANA
(1) OJ No C 287, 30. 10. 1995.
(2) The date of entry into force of the Protocol will be published in the Official Journal of the  European Communities by the General Secretariat of the Council.
